headline: Should You Rethink Your Position on Jabil After a 51% Surge in 2024?
summary: Trying to decide what to do with Jabil stock right now? You are not alone. After rallying an incredible 51.1% so far this year and racking up a 76.8% gain over the last twelve months, the stock has become a magnet for investors looking for growth opportunities. Pull back the lens even further, and the longer-term numbers—up a staggering 541.1% in five years—show just how strong Jabil's push has been.
